The paper also deals with Markov decision processes, which are related to control systems, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a likely sub-category as well. The use of neural networks suggests that cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) could also be a relevant sub-category. Finally, the paper presents a convergence rate analysis, which is related to theoretical computer science, making cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) a possible sub-category.
